Class LinkServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<LinkComponentType,Link>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.link.LinkServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ButtonService, LinkService, TableInsertion
public class LinkServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<LinkComponentType,Link> implements LinkService
Implementation of the LinkService interface providing actions for interacting with link components. Extends AbstractComponentService to handle operations on Link components.
